{"tid":447599,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"《馬卡報》2017年度最差陣容","createTime":"2017-10-25T12:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T17:15:16.000Z","uid":60286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c43804c40cbcc147286cea439499c6ccfeeb5424","tid":447599,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/202133_d702cee9442b84912c86c7a92777ee1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F202133_d702cee9442b84912c86c7a92777ee1a.png&h=0d0b389e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日國際足協(FIFA)在英國倫敦舉行了一年一度的頒獎典禮，其中C朗拿度再次壓倒美斯，奪得世界足球先生寶座，而年度最佳11人亦一併被選出來。而就在這頒獎禮過後，著名體育媒體《馬卡報》亦選出了2017年的一套最差陣容，陣容中竟然發現3名巴塞隆拿的球員。<br />\n<br />\n今次這份最差陣容名單中，一共有3人來自巴塞隆拿、2人來自巴黎聖日耳門、2人來自曼城，而皇馬、拜仁、熱刺及士砵亭則各有1人入選。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/202219_b8275ae4860bed00dde3a8ed9fe04ff5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F202219_b8275ae4860bed00dde3a8ed9fe04ff5.jpg&h=f3a97a11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年度最差陣容:<br />\n前鋒：謝斯(巴黎聖日耳門)、艾卡沙(巴塞隆拿)、贊臣(熱刺)<br />\n中場：安祖高美斯(巴塞)、基祖維克(巴黎聖日耳門)、連拿度山齊士(拜仁慕尼黑)、加坦(馬體會)<br />\n後衛：干查奧(士砵亭)、馬菲奧(巴塞隆拿)、史東斯(曼城)<br />\n門將：巴禾(曼城)<br />\n<br />\n來源：球迷世界"},{"pid":"ac77f83e91355cce47cc949a5d079ddb8cfdbc38","tid":447599,"uid":11254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:24:26.000Z","msg":"巴我咁勁都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e3ae46faa781142d722adc3ffd01f7401a07e4","tid":447599,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:26:54.000Z","msg":"我地巴塞有3個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f65f8950c17f9db22b69b8213cd36b3290bcc01","tid":447599,"uid":106115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:29:09.000Z","m